====================================================\
5.3 AUTHENTICATION AND USER MODELS\
====================================================\
\
model User \{\
  id            String      @id @default(uuid())\
  name          String\
  email         String      @unique\
  passwordHash  String\
  role          Role        @default(EDITOR)\
  image         String?\
  isActive      Boolean     @default(true)\
\
  createdAt     DateTime    @default(now())\
  updatedAt     DateTime    @updatedAt\
\
  accounts      Account[]\
  sessions      Session[]\
  auditLogs     AuditLog[]\
\}\
\
model Account \{\
  id                 String  @id @default(uuid())\
  userId             String\
  type               String\
  provider           String\
  providerAccountId  String\
  refresh_token      String?\
  access_token       String?\
  expires_at         Int?\
  token_type         String?\
  scope              String?\
  id_token           String?\
  session_state      String?\
\
  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)\
\
  @@unique([provider, providerAccountId])\
\}\
\
model Session \{\
  id            String   @id @default(uuid())\
  sessionToken  String   @unique\
  userId        String\
  expires       DateTime\
\
  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)\
\}\
\
model VerificationToken \{\
  identifier String\
  token      String   @unique\
  expires    DateTime\
\
  @@unique([identifier, token])\
\}\
\
Rules:\
\
- Passwords must be hashed.\
- Plain-text password storage is prohibited.\
- Admin routes must be protected.\
- RBAC must be enforced server-side.\
- Viewer role must remain read-only.\
- Editor role must not manage users.\
- Admin role has full access.\
\
====================================================\
5.4 AUDIT AND VERSIONING MODELS\
====================================================\
\
model AuditLog \{\
  id          String      @id @default(uuid())\
  userId      String?\
  action      AuditAction\
  entityType  String?\
  entityId    String?\
  details     String      @db.Text\
  ipAddress   String?\
  userAgent   String?\
  createdAt   DateTime    @default(now())\
\
  user User? @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])\
\}\
\
model ContentVersion \{\
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())\
  entityType  String\
  entityId    String\
  version     Int\
  payload     Json\
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())\
  createdBy   String?\
\}\
\
Audit logging must track:\
\
- Create\
- Update\
- Delete\
- Publish\
- Archive\
- Rollback\
- Login\
- Permission changes\
\
Versioning must support:\
\
- Content snapshots\
- Publishing history\
- Rollback readiness\
