====================================================\
8. LEAD MANAGEMENT SYSTEM\
====================================================\
\
Lead management is a core business function.\
\
All lead capture points must flow into a centralized lead system.\
\
Sources include:\
\
- Homepage CTA\
- Contact Forms\
- Event Registrations\
- Service Pages\
- Case Studies\
- Calendly Flows\
- Future Commerce Flows\
\
====================================================\
8.1 LEADS\
====================================================\
\
model Lead \{\
  id                String      @id @default(uuid())\
\
  firstName         String\
  lastName          String\
\
  email             String\
  phone             String?\
\
  grade             Grade?\
\
  country           String?\
\
  source            String?\
\
  status            LeadStatus  @default(NEW)\
\
  notes             String?     @db.Text\
\
  assignedToId      String?\
\
  createdAt         DateTime    @default(now())\
  updatedAt         DateTime    @updatedAt\
\}\
\
====================================================\
8.2 LEAD TIMELINE\
====================================================\
\
model LeadActivity \{\
  id                String      @id @default(uuid())\
\
  leadId            String\
\
  activityType      String\
\
  description       String      @db.Text\
\
  createdAt         DateTime    @default(now())\
\}\
\
Lead timeline examples:\
\
- Lead Created\
- Email Sent\
- Phone Call\
- Consultation Scheduled\
- Lead Qualified\
- Lead Converted\
- Lead Closed\
